{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe it came into being after the-- after 1919 or 1920, as early as that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or certainly in the early '20s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the paradoxical situation arose as a result of it, that because in Hungary, even well before the war-- I was born in '24.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If a Jewish intellectual wanted to pursue tertiary education, sometimes he had to go to Berlin, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before Hitler, right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in Hungary, the numerous clauses restricted the Jewish participation to I think 6%.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you want to go to university?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course I wanted to go to university.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- you asked me about my-- my-- my high school days, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anti-Semitism during that, is that correct?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, now we are entering into-- into-- I matriculated in 1942, which was already an advanced stage of the war, and certainly an advanced stage of the German influence in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The local population's reactions should be, perhaps, explained, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism in Hungary was a fairly inherent issue in the population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hungary was an unfortunate country, unfortunate from the point of view that it always managed to attached itself to the loser.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the First World War, they managed to lose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Second World War, eventually they lost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when you are-- that-- that had a stronger influence on the Hungarian historical times in the '20s and '30s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when a country is-- is-- is defeated, you're always looking for-- for scapegoats.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Jews became the scapegoats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were becoming the reason, plausible reason why a lot of the setbacks have occurred.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it-- like any minority in a-- in a-- in a-- in a country, times were not as liberal as here today in Australia, where anything and everybody goes.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
